'''Sanctum Arcti''' was [[Calius saj Leeloo]]'s most famous structure. During a [[Groundquake/Legends|groundquake]] in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], it suffered only minor damage, and was considered a miracle by the galactic community.

